text: Marysette Agnel (28 August 1926 - 19 July 1958) was a French alpine skier. She competed at the 1952 Winter Olympics and the 1956 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1926 births Category:1958 deaths Category:French female alpine skiers Category:Olympic alpine skiers of France Category:Alpine skiers at the 1952 Winter Olympics Category:Alpine skiers at the 1956 Winter Olympics Category:People from Chamonix Category:Sportspeople from Haute-Savoie
